And while doing Tanner's survey, vote on one more travel related question below! :airplane:

If we were to fly out in two different groups (but still fly home on same flight together), which option below would you be more interested in? You're not committed to your vote at this point, just polling!

> :one: - Fly out of SLC on morning of Jan 1 and get an extra day in the Philippines.
> :two: - Fly out of SLC on morning of Jan 2.
> :no_entry_sign: - Neither are great. Something else, please (add a comment)

text:
Jazz Game Details:
*If you can no longer come, please let me know ASAP so we can find someone else to fill your spot*

Date/Time: Thursday Nov 2, 7pm (this is next Thursday)
Logistics: *We are going to have a group taking the 5:16pm FrontRunner (free with your BYU ID) from Provo.* If you would like to drive yourself to the Delta Center, you are responsible for your own parking.

*Please message me (or comment in this thread) the email address you would like your ticket sent to.* You will be prompted to create (or sign into) a SeatGeek account to access the ticket, so if you have a SeatGeek account already send me the email associated with it.
